{"tid":1041795,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"CJ7聯賽知名度高 逾200隊4,000人參與","createTime":"2019-03-01T06:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T09:29:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5498769bc34ac381983756a587ccebece134419b","tid":1041795,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190301/20623579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190301%2F20623579&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMBw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=234c1c24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190301%2F20623579&h=8667f084\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190301/20623579</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCJ7聯賽知名度高<br />\n逾200隊4,000人參與<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190301/large/a0303a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190301%2Flarge%2Fa0303a.jpg&h=9c1cf436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCJ7官網發公告，稱「因有急事，抱歉，3月的賽事需要取消」。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】不法集團被揭涉以舉辦業餘聯賽為名，盜取參賽者身份證資料製作假身份證謀利，據悉由涉案集團舉辦的「CJ7人足球聯賽」，參賽球隊逾200隊，以每隊約20人推算，有逾4,000人參加。賽會網頁昨發公告，指由昨日起至下月賽事「因有急事」需取消；而賽會fb專頁及其他網上資料亦已被刪除。<br />\n<br />\nCJ7是本地其中一個著名業餘聯賽，官網介紹他們於2013年成立。今屆舉辦包括平日聯賽、周末聯賽及草地聯賽等22項賽事，聯賽設升降制，除其中三項，每項賽事均有10隊球隊參加，據官網資料則至少共213球隊參賽；每隊報名由10多人至30人不等，即共逾4,000人參與。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：足球場難求11人場$278炒上$1,200<br />\n<br />\n球員希望賽會交代<br />\n<br />\n根據CJ7今屆草地足球聯賽報名資料，球隊報名費為1.1萬元，每屆有20至22場賽事，費用包括場地及拍片服務。聯賽亦設有YouTube頻道，上載賽事片段。有參與CJ7聯賽球員表示，原本昨晚有比賽，但昨晨才收到賽事取消通知，他不知道個人資料有否被盜用，希望賽會早日交代。<br />\n<br />\n■記者徐雲庭  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n足球場難求 11人場$278炒上$1,200<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n幣少爺涉串謀詐騙被捕 凍結500萬資產<br />\n<br />\n足球場難求11人場$278炒上$1,200<br />\n足球賽搞手盜參賽者資料 製124高仿身份證訂康文署場狂炒賺百萬"},{"pid":"af729467859d3c91ec2c2e83e2d65185a86835fa","tid":1041795,"uid":84702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317ba2de0ccaf6719881dfae5ca888f3e9b96754","tid":1041795,"uid":55851,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"好多阿叔同MK當踢英超咁爭住報名比人偷資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a03d2205e443a0d72b7437abc133e3cc6ca9f8","tid":1041795,"uid":76988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"Cj又開始搞返，有回應未？"},{"pid":"1589b90333c5a3e285ee8048ed7d02ca6818c8ef","tid":1041795,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87a03d2205e443a0d72b7437abc133e3cc6ca9f8","tid":1041795,"uid":76988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"Cj又開始搞返，有回應未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"無得比人退錢<br />\nOn9"},{"pid":"2c5f4a4f1fc5fbd19cc6bdf6ce68146e6641efdc","tid":1041795,"uid":3630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"好似有人接左手"},{"pid":"520c67f6209ea2b13fb63225979f366fadf1ef3b","tid":1041795,"uid":76988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"錢銀事少，唔交代d個人資料去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做左d非法野點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a4412bfc5795c1a5be76bcfe08d4252fbb7509","tid":1041795,"uid":21190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"仆街 參加左兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.p